### Create a transaction
POST http://localhost:5092/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "Transfer"
}

###

### List all transactions
GET http://localhost:5092/transactions

###

### Filter by account
GET http://localhost:5092/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

###

### Filter by type and date range
GET http://localhost:5092/transactions?type=Transfer&from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31

###

### Get transaction by ID
GET http://localhost:5092/transactions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###

### Get account balance
GET http://localhost:5092/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

###

### Get account summary
GET http://localhost:5092/accounts/ACC-12345/summary
